without them knowing of it.

9
00:00:25,166 --> 00:00:28,384
<i>If you do not return the
entirety of the hidden cache,</i>

10
00:00:28,419 --> 00:00:30,252
know that Nassau will
likely burn for it.

11
00:00:30,305 --> 00:00:32,054
With everything I've
lost in recent days,

12
00:00:32,090 --> 00:00:33,889
