13
00:00:33,925 --> 00:00:35,591
<i>We walk into the tavern,
we sign our names,</i>

14
00:00:35,643 --> 00:00:38,477
<i>and then not only are we square
with the law our money is, too.</i>

15
00:00:38,513 --> 00:00:40,980
The wound should be far further
along towards quietening itself.

16
