62
00:05:30,354 --> 00:05:33,305
It's a fucking lashing.
I know how to tie it.

63
00:05:33,307 --> 00:05:36,692
If he tied it wrong, then
you instructed him wrong.

64
00:05:40,865 --> 00:05:42,865
<i>You listen to me.</i>

65
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:46,368
We persuaded them that they need us.

66
00:05:46,404 --> 00:05:47,820
We most certainly need them.

67
00:05:47,872 --> 00:05:50,656
Do you understand what I'm saying?

68
00:05:56,547 --> 00:05:58,998
<i>[men shouting]</i>

69
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,916
- [grunts]
- <i>[thuds]</i>

70
00:06:04,255 --> 00:06:06,755
Don't imagine that will
be the last of those.

71
00:06:08,817 --> 00:06:10,045
Neither do I.

72
00:06:12,179 --> 00:06:14,346
So how exactly do you see this working?

73
00:06:15,679 --> 00:06:17,671
